zip/unzips
- Initial : zip -rq Example_backup important_file/
- ONGOING : zip -uq Example_backup.zip
- RECOVERY: unzip  $HOME/Example_backup.zip  #does not restore to absolute location (add option to choose directory to cd into before running and umask (for file permission))
- SHOW    : unzip -Z Example_backup.zip 
